longBusinessSummary: Studentbostäder i Norden AB (publ) owns, develops, and manages student housing properties in long term partnerships with municipalities, regions, and universities in Sweden. The company provides student accommodation, and fully digitized rental management services. Studentbostäder i Norden AB (publ) was incorporated in 2006 and is headquartered in Uppsala, Sweden.
